- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is another possible category as the paper deals with finite automata and their use in solving linear arithmetic problems. 
- cs.SC (Symbolic Computation) is a possible category as the paper deals with symbolic manipulation of linear arithmetic expressions. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is also a possible category as the paper deals with automata on infinite words, which is a topic in formal languages and automata theory.
